#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:2
msgid "Add a cascading hydropower system"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:4
msgid ""
"**Goal.** Introduce a multi-station hydropower cascade (e.g. a new river "
"basin) into a scenario, with per-station reservoir physics and inter-"
"station water-delay routing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/how_to/add_a_cascading_hydropower_system.rst:8
msgid ""
"This is the heaviest \"add a tech\" recipe because hydropower stations "
"are first-class techs in PREP-SHOT (not aggregated). Each station is its "
"own row in ``tech_registry.csv`` AND has its own reservoir- parameter "
"rows across ~10 reservoir-specific files. See the shipped Lower Mekong "
"scenario (``examples/southeast_asia``, 57 stations) and the Thailand "
"scenario (``examples/thailand``, 13 stations) for fully-worked examples."
msgstr ""

